subject: Fix regression in swift store functional test

messages.message: Uploaded patch set 1.

Patch Set 1:

This patches fixes the immediate regression in the test, although not all test cases pass for me locally.  However, this does get most of them back into a working state.

https://gist.github.com/bdelliott/9fa6de87fca376f00323

I suspect these tests have suffered from lack of maintenance over time, but someone more familiar may know better.
